  "title": "Stellaris StellarView Compatibility Resourcepack",
  "description": "Overrides Stellaris planet sky with StellarView sky",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stellaris-stellarview-compatibility\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1482048?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&color=626e7b&label=CurseForge\" alt=\"Curseforge\"></a>\n[![GitHub](https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=github)](https://github.com/lukaskabc/Stellaris-StellarView-Compatibility)\n[![Modrinth mod version](https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/SrNny2Go?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&color=626e7b&label=Mod%20version)](https://modrinth.com/mod/stellaris-stellarview-compatibility)\n\nDisables Stellaris custom sky and configures StellarView sky for every planet.\n\nThere are two formats of the compatibility - Mod or Resourcepack.\nThey are identical, but with mod format you get automatic dependency validation from neoforge.\n\n## Dependencies\n\n<table>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>StellarView Mixin Renderer</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/lukaskabc/StellarViewMixinRenderer/\">\n          <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=GitHub\" alt=\"GitHub\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/stellar-view-mixin-renderer\">\n          <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Modrinth-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stellar-view-mixin-renderer\">\n          <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/CurseForge-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge\" alt=\"CurseForge\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Stellaris</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/st0x0ef/stellaris/\">\n          <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=GitHub\" alt=\"GitHub\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/stellaris\">\n          <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Modrinth-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stellaris\">\n          <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/CurseForge-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge\" alt=\"CurseForge\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>StellarView</td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/Povstalec/stellarview/\">\n          <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=GitHub\" alt=\"GitHub\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/stellarview\">\n          <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Modrinth-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <a href=\"https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stellarview\">\n          <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/CurseForge-grey?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge\" alt=\"CurseForge\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n## Implemented planets/dimensions\n\n- Earth (overworld)\n- Earth Orbit\n- Jupiter\n- Mars\n- Mars Orbit\n- Mercury\n- Mercury Orbit\n- Moon\n- Venus\n- Venus Orbit",
